  "description": "Ram Bahadur Thapa (Nepali: राम बहादुर थापा), also known by his nom de guerre Badal, is a Nepali politician currently serving as the vice president of the CPN (UML). He has held several key ministerial positions, including Minister for Home Affairs from 2018 to 2021 and Minister of Defence from 2008 to 2009. He was also a member of the National Assembly representing Bagmati Province. Thapa previously served as the General Secretary of the Communist Party of Nepal (Maoist Centre).",
